nodes.bodyText:
I think you also need to filter out empty dirs, no?



      bnd/biz.aQute.bndlib/src/aQute/bnd/osgi/Jar.java


        Lines 1018 to 1021
      in
      6c127ce







           public List<String> getPackages() { 




           	check(); 




           	return MapStream.of(directories) 




           		.filterValue(mdir -> Objects.nonNull(mdir) && !mdir.isEmpty()) 





It is possible a resource is added which creates a directory and later the resource is removed. This is why getPackages() filters out empty directories.

